{"id":19790,"title":"Overcoming the current deadlock in antibiotic research.","abstract":"Antibiotic-resistant bacteria are on the rise, making it harder to treat bacterial infections. The situation is aggravated by the shrinking of the antibiotic development pipeline. To finance urgently needed incentives for antibiotic research, creative financing solutions are needed. Public-private partnerships (PPPs) are a successful model for moving forward. ","date":"2014-04-04","categories":"Bacterial Infections and Mycoses","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24698433","annotations":[{"name":"Research","weight":0.550962,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Research"},{"name":"Finance","weight":0.54001,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Finance"},{"name":"Bacteria","weight":0.132246,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bacteria"},{"name":"Infection","weight":0.0937821,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infection"},{"name":"Antibacterial","weight":0.0574785,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antibacterial"},{"name":"Partnership","weight":0.0391252,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Partnership"},{"name":"Incentive","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Incentive"},{"name":"Model (person)","weight":0.0300804,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Model_(person)"},{"name":"Creative financing","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Creative_financing"},{"name":"International development","weight":0.0219197,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_development"},{"name":"Pipeline transport","weight":0.0175445,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pipeline_transport"},{"name":"Deadlock","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deadlock"},{"name":"Forward (association football)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wi